text.tspan: How am I feeling right now?
Did I follow my plans for today (and if not, why not) ?
What could I have done better?
Did I express my gratefulness to someone?
Did I do something out of my ordinary daily agenda?
What was the best thing that happened to me today?
What was the biggest moment of unhappiness for you today?
What/whom did I make better today?
What is one thing I've accomplished?
Did I do my best to be happy today?
What is the most important thing I must accomplish tomorrow?
What one thing must I focus on this week?
